Viewer
======
- continuous view: show all cells of table (viewer) with some initial size and don't show content yet
    * continuous horizontal layout is [0, 1]
    * continuous vertical layout is [1, 0]

TextEdit
========
- use CodeMirror for TextEdit: http://marijnhaverbeke.nl/git/codemirror

LineEdit
========
- input element - increase "size" attribute to fit the text

